{"tid":871402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［搞走塑］其實除左環保之外，衛生常識都好重要","createTime":"2018-10-22T02:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T02:10:33.000Z","uid":109136,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"71a24f4b705504213cf2f036f19a87053c04f7a1","tid":871402,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/100149_1b46a88565443e8deae4c80c2c3c41db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F100149_1b46a88565443e8deae4c80c2c3c41db.png&h=3982f4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解調味料要有獨立包裝？<br />\n咪就係有d撚屌拎埋糖盅隻奠攪自己杯野<br />\n有d仲要奶埋隻羹再放入去囉<br />\n早排先有個阿伯就係咁俾人打死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/100424_f0c7a075ad44fa75084a33a9fc833b4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F100424_f0c7a075ad44fa75084a33a9fc833b4f.png&h=6ae27998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買面包用自備袋<br />\n無問題<br />\n但你咁大條法包就咁暴露係空氣外面<br />\n其實會痴左好多塵同污染物<br />\n到時食到肚痛唔好賴人地唔乾淨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/100633_490b574a5ae3f9efbeb1b7d1d6be52c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F100633_490b574a5ae3f9efbeb1b7d1d6be52c0.png&h=77aa6ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/100636_dfab63bcc179085641e26958b7b23f51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F100636_dfab63bcc179085641e26958b7b23f51.png&h=b32f18fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個就最on9<br />\n食落肚既野梗係衛生行先嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉都廢事入去教精佢地"},{"pid":"6affc38